name: MAN IS THE MOON
description:
"..we almost got there" The third
and final piece in the genesis
series by Raoul Marks, explores
ambition and loss. Featuring the
'OG Astro' in full motion, this
unique work parallels the lengths
that we, and by implication the
human species, will go to reach for
the impossible. Sometimes we get
there, sometimes we fall short.
